{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":98,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他们在他们的主那里的报酬是：[住在]诸河流过的乐园，永居其中。安拉喜悦他们，他们敬爱安拉。这是为畏惧他的主的人预备的。"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"当大地强烈震动[注]，"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"当大地抛出其重担时，"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"人将说：“大地怎么啦？”"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"在那日，大地将报告自己的消息[大地上曾发生的善恶]，"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"因为你的主已启示它。"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"在那日，人类将分批出现，以便他们看见自己的行为[的报酬]。"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"谁做了一个原子之重的善事[注]，谁将见其善报；"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"谁做了一个原子之重的恶事，谁将见其恶报。"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以奔驰而喘息的战马、"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"蹄发火花、"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"黎明时突袭、"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"卷起漫天灰尘、"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"迅速攻入敌阵的战马发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"人[不信仰者]对自己的主总是忘恩负义的。"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"他[的行为]确是见证此事[忘恩负义]的。"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他的确非常贪爱财富。"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"难道他不知道吗？当坟墓中的一切被揭露[死人被复活]、"}]}